          "code": "SinOsc a => Gain ag => Gain mix => dac;\nSinOsc b => Gain bg => mix;\n0.55 => ag.gain; 0.35 => bg.gain;\nwhile (true) { 220 => a.freq; 330 => b.freq; 0.16 * hostStateGain * hostTrackGain => mix.gain; 1::samp => now; }",
