          "code": "TriOsc t => Gain g => dac;\nwhile (true) { 440 + (Math.sin(hostGlobalBeat * 0.12) * 18) => t.freq; 0.10 * (0.55 + (0.45 * hostBarPhase)) * hostStateGain * hostTrackGain => g.gain; 1::samp => now; }",
