          "phase": 0,
          "gain": 0.2,
          "muted": false,
          "soloed": false,
          "code": "giSine ftgen 1, 0, 4096, 10, 1\ninstr 1\n kfreq chnget \"hostFreq\"\n kgain chnget \"hostGain\"\n ktrack chnget \"hostTrackGain\"\n kstate chnget \"hostStateGain\"\n kbeat chnget \"hostStateBeat\"\n kenv = exp(-frac(kbeat * 0.5) * 5)\n a1 oscili kgain * ktrack * kstate * 0.18 * kenv, kfreq * 6, giSine\n outs a1, a1\nendin",
